<html>

<head>
  <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Fjalla+One' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Quicksand:300' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>

</head>

<body style="margin: 0;">

<div class="header" style="width:100%; height: auto;">
  <img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com/bikeblackspot2015/static_resources/banner.png" style="width: 100%; height: auto; background-size: cover; display: block;"/>
</div>

<div class="container" style="width: 100%; height: auto; text-align: center;">

  <div class="message" style="width: 100%; height: 0 auto; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3%;">
    <h1 style="font-family: 'Fjalla One', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="color:##21BED8;">THANKYOU FOR REPORTING YOUR</span> &nbsp;BIKE BLACK SPOT</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="map" style="width: 60%; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;"><img style="width: 100%" src="<%= google_map %>">
  </div>

  <div class="message" style="width: 100%; height: 0 auto; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3%;">
    <h1 style="font-family: 'Fjalla One', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">
      <span style="color: #21BED8;"><%= name %> <%= last %></span>&nbsp;<%= date %></h1>
  </div>

  <div class="report" style="width: 56%; height: auto; padding: 2%; background-color: #eee; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; overflow: auto;">

    <div class="info" style="width: 60%; float: left; text-align: left; ">
      <h3 style="font-family: 'Fjalla One', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; padding-right: 10px;"><%= title %></h3>

      <h3 style="font-family: 'Fjalla One', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">
        <span style="color: #21BED8; padding-right: 10px;"><%= address %></span></h3>

      <p style="font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif; padding-right: 10px;"><%= description %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="image" style="float: right; width: 40%;">
      <div class="photo" style="float: right;">
        <img style="max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; padding-top: 10%;" src="<%= photo %>">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="message" style="width: 100%; height: 0 auto; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3%;">
      <h1 style="font-family: 'Fjalla One', sans-serif;"><span>WHAT HAPPENS NEXT?</span></h1>

      <div class="text2" style="width: 60%; height: auto; font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif; text-align: left; margin: auto;">
      <p style="font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif;">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Quisque maximus eros non dapibus auctor. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Mauris vitae orci dui. Vestibulum enim velit, hendrerit a viverra eu, congue sit amet mi. 
        Quisque maximus, odio et consectetur consequat, dolor massa faucibus elit, fermentum gravida tellus tortor et nisi. Donec eu tempus sem. Etiam cursus, justo sit amet pretium varius, nisi sem porta purus, id blandit diam eros quis metus.
      </p>
      </div>

      <div class="social" style="list-style: none; text-decoration: none; margin-top: 3%; text-align: center;">
        <li>
          <a href="#" style="padding: 0.5%;"><img src="images/facebook.png"></a>
          <a href="#" style="padding: 0.5%;"><img src="images/twitter.png"></a>
          <a href="#" style="padding: 0.5%;"><img src="images/email.png"></a>
          <a href="#" style="padding: 0.5%;"><img src="images/linkedin.png"></a>
        </li>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <footer style="font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 0 auto; padding-top: 3%; padding-bottom: 3%;">

    <div class="disc">
      <div class="text" style="width: 32%; margin: 0 auto; padding-top: 10px; text-align: center;">
        <img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com/bikeblackspot2015/static_resources/greens.jpg" style="width: 10%; padding-right: 2%; float: left;">
        <span>This is a campaign of the Australian Greens. Authorised by Senator Janet Rice, 240 Sydney Rd Coburg VIC 3058.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </footer>

</div>

</body>

</html>